description:
Microsoft Team Foundation Server Extended Client

Integrate with Microsoft Team Foundation Server and Visual Studio Team Services from desktop-based Windows applications.  Work with and manage version control, work items, and build, and other resources from your client application.  The extended client is a thicker client object model which includes wrappers for SOAP APIs that may not have a corresponding REST end point available yet.  This package is equivalent to the TFS Object Model MSI available for previous versions of Visual Studio.

Versions 14.89.x correspond to Visual Studio 2015 Update 1.
title: Microsoft Team Foundation Server Extended Client
